message: Hi Bob, I'm looking to sell this product which I believe would be highly valuable to you. I'm offering it at $13,000.
Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I was thinking of something more around $9,500. Would you be willing to consider that?
Hi Bob, thanks for your offer. I understand your perspective, but $9,500 is a bit too low for me.  Could you do $11,500?
Hi Alice, I understand your perspective, but $11,500 is still a bit higher than I'm willing to pay. Would you be willing to consider $10,800?
